graph LR
    LlamaStackOp[Llama Stack K8s Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    LlamaStackOp -->|orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes 1.20+]
    LlamaStackOp -->|controller framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.17+]
    LlamaStackOp -->|metrics auth| KubeRBACProxy[kube-rbac-proxy v0.15.0]
    LlamaStackOp -->|manifest rendering| Kustomize[Kustomize v4+]
    LlamaStackOp -->|manages images| LlamaStackDist[Llama Stack Distribution v0.3.5]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    LlamaStackOp -.->|OpenShift only| OpenshiftSCC[OpenShift SCC anyuid]
    LlamaStackOp -.->|metrics scraping| PrometheusOp[Prometheus ServiceMonitor]
    LlamaStackOp -.->|TLS certificates| CertManager[cert-manager]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    LlamaStackOp -->|UI management| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    LlamaStackOp -->|TLS CA bundle| TrustedCABundle[ODH Trusted CA Bundle]
    LlamaStackOp -.->|model metadata| ModelRegistry[Model Registry]
    LlamaStackOp -.->|inference backend| InferenceServices[Inference Services<br/>vLLM, Ollama]

    %% External Services (Runtime)
    LlamaStackOp -->|image registry| ContainerRegistry[Container Registry<br/>quay.io/docker.io]
    LlamaStackOp -.->|model downloads| HuggingFace[HuggingFace Hub]

    %% Integration Points
    DataSciencePipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|auto-deploy models| LlamaStackOp
    Dashboard -->|creates CRs| LlamaStackOp

    %% Llama Stack Server Dependencies (Created by Operator)
    subgraph "Llama Stack Server Runtime"
        LlamaServer[Llama Stack Server]
        LlamaServer -->|calls| vLLM[vLLM Inference<br/>8000/TCP]
        LlamaServer -->|calls| Ollama[Ollama Inference<br/>11434/TCP]
        LlamaServer -->|downloads| HuggingFace
        LlamaServer -.->|queries| ModelRegistry
    end

    LlamaStackOp -.->|deploys & manages| LlamaServer

    %% Styling
    style LlamaStackOp fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px
    style K8s fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ControllerRuntime fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style KubeRBACProxy fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Kustomize fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style LlamaStackDist fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style OpenshiftSCC fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style PrometheusOp fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style CertManager fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style TrustedCABundle fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style ModelRegistry fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style InferenceServices fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style DataSciencePipelines fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style ContainerRegistry fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style HuggingFace fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style LlamaServer fill:#b8e986,stroke:#333
    style vLLM fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Ollama fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
